{
  "text": "The current experimental limit on the anomalous magnetic moment of the tau lepton is rather weak, but it can be improved in the future [CITATION_1] :",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "119207374"
  },
  "bib_entries": {
    "119207374": {
      "title": "Towards a determination of the tau lepton dipole moments",
      "abstract": "The τ anomalous magnetic moment aτ and electric dipole moment dτ have not yet been observed. The present bounds on their values are of order 10−2 and 10−17e cm, respectively. We propose to measure aτ with a precision of O(10−3) or better and improve the existing limits on dτ using precise τ−→l−ντν¯lγ (l=e or μ) data from high-luminosity B factories. A detailed feasibility study of this method is underway."
    }
  }
}